{"words":[{"word":"ow","count":3},{"word":"alright","count":2},{"word":"okay","count":2},{"word":"oh","count":2},{"word":"yes","count":2},{"word":"seen","count":2},{"word":"uniform","count":2},{"word":"tossed","count":2},{"word":"easy","count":2},{"word":"remember","count":2},{"word":"boss","count":1},{"word":"give","count":1},{"word":"i-induction","count":1},{"word":"cell","count":1},{"word":"never","count":1},{"word":"heard","count":1},{"word":"tds","count":1},{"word":"coming","count":1},{"word":"lot","count":1},{"word":"days","count":1},{"word":"saw","count":1},{"word":"getting","count":1},{"word":"into","count":1},{"word":"huge","count":1},{"word":"fight","count":1},{"word":"guys","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"fighting","count":1},{"word":"big","count":1},{"word":"tin","count":1},{"word":"box","count":1},{"word":"crazy","count":1},{"word":"thought","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"kind","count":1},{"word":"treasure","count":1},{"word":"brought","count":1},{"word":"everything","count":1},{"word":"went","count":1},{"word":"quite","count":1},{"word":"figure","count":1},{"word":"life","count":1},{"word":"used","count":1},{"word":"aside","count":1},{"word":"hey","count":1},{"word":"buddy","count":1},{"word":"i-i","count":1},{"word":"since","count":1},{"word":"eek","count":1},{"word":"swear","count":1},{"word":"probably","count":1},{"word":"pile","count":1},{"word":"yeah","count":1},{"word":"someone","count":1},{"word":"wore","count":1},{"word":"always","count":1},{"word":"repairing","count":1},{"word":"stuff","count":1},{"word":"near","count":1},{"word":"surveillance","count":1},{"word":"station","count":1},{"word":"lately","count":1},{"word":"though","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Ow, ow, ow! Alright, Alright! I get it, Boss. I give up, okay!?","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"I-Induction Cell? We've never even heard of it before.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Oh! That! Yes, yes. We’ve seen it before.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"The TDs’ been coming over here a lot these days. And we saw them getting into a huge fight with those uniform guys the other day.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"They were fighting over that big tin box like crazy. We thought it must be some kind of treasure, and brought it back after everything went all quite.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Couldn’t figure out for the life of us what it was or used for, so we just tossed it aside.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Hey! Easy, easy buddy! I-I don’t remember where it is. It’s been a while since we tossed it. Okay...?","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Eek! I swear, I can’t remember!","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Why... why don’t you go look for it yourself? It’s probably in that pile over there.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004},{"text":"Oh, yeah. There was someone who wore the same uniform as you and was always repairing stuff near the surveillance station. Haven't seen them lately, though.","quest_name":"Restart the radar","quest_id":122000004}]}